quran[15]{c,v,t,f}:
  37,79,"Ntendele uŵe kwa Nuhu mu iwumbe yosope."
  37,80,"Chisimu Uwwe iyyoyopeyo ni yatukutiji pakwalipila ŵakolosya."
  37,81,"Chisimu jwalakwe (Nuhu) jwaliji mwa achikapolo Ŵetu ŵakulupilila."
  38,58,"Ni (ipotesi) yine yanti chisawu iyyiyi yamitundumitundu."
  38,59,"(Tachisalilidwa akukuyidwa pakuponyedwa kumoto pamo ni akukuya): “Awu ni nkutula waukwinjila pamo ni jenumanja (ku Moto).” (Akukuyidwa tachiti): “Ŵangali pakwichila pambone ŵanganyao. Chisimu ŵanganyao tapye Moto.”"
  38,60,"(Akukuya) tachiti: “Nambo jenumanja ni ŵankuŵajilwa ngakola pakwichila pambone, jenumanja ni ŵantutendekasyisye uwwe kupata ayi (ipotesiyi pakutusochelesya ku duniya), basi kaje kusakala malo gakutamilichika gakwe!”"
  39,43,"Ana kapena alitendele (inepe) yangaŵaga Allah kuŵa yakwachondelela (kwa Allah)? Jilani: “Ana nantimuno ili yangali ulamusi pa chilichose soni yangali lunda?”"
  39,44,"Jilani: “Chondechonde chosope chili kwa (malamusi ga) Allah, uŵele Wakwe uchimwene wa kumawunde ni petaka, kaneka Kukwakwe tinchiuchisyidwa.”"
  39,45,"Sano pati achikolanjidwaga Allah Jikape jikasanyalaisyidwaga mitima ja aŵala ŵangakukulupilila ya Akhera, nambo pati achikolanjidwaga aŵala ŵanganaŵa Jwalakwe, jele ndemajo ŵanganyao akasasengwaga."
  40,22,"Yalakweyi nilogongo lyanti ŵanganyao ŵaliji nkwaichilila Achimitenga ŵao ni ilosyo yakuonechela ni ŵaakaaniile, basi Allah niŵakwembekenye. Chisimu Jwalakwe ni Jwakulimbangana nnope, Jwaukali kusyene pakupeleka ipotesi."
  40,23,"Soni chisimu chene twantumisye Musa ni isimosimo Yetu kwisa soni maumboni gakuonechela."
  40,24,"Kwa Firiauna, Hamana ni Karuna, ŵanganyao ni ŵatite: “(Aju ni) nsaŵi, jwaunami kusyene.”"
  41,1,"Hâ. Mîm. ",footnotes:1:Asi harufusi ni chimpepe mu isimosimo ya Qur’an. Ni pangali jwine jwaakumanyilila mate gakwe ikaŵeje Allah pe basi.
  41,2,"Chakutulusyidwa (chalakwechi) chityochele kwa (Allah) Jwaukoto wejinji, Jwachanasa channope."
  41,3,"(Chalakwechi ni) Chitabu chagasalichisyidwe ma Ȃya gakwe, Qur’an jacharabu, (gasalichisyidwe ma Ȃya gakwe) ku ŵandu ŵaakumanyilila (Maulama)."